@startuml Org_Structure
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 10

rectangle "根组织 (ROOT)\ntagId: ROOT" <<#FFE0B2>> as ROOT

rectangle "技术部\nDEPT_TECH" <<#B3E5FC>> as TECH
rectangle "运营部\nDEPT_OPS" <<#B3E5FC>> as OPS
rectangle "市场部\nDEPT_MKT" <<#B3E5FC>> as MKT

rectangle "后端组\nTECH_BE" <<#C8E6C9>>
rectangle "前端组\nTECH_FE" <<#C8E6C9>>
rectangle "AI组\nTECH_AI" <<#C8E6C9>>
rectangle "行政组\nOPS_A" <<#C8E6C9>>
rectangle "策划组\nMKT_PLAN" <<#C8E6C9>>

ROOT --> TECH
ROOT --> OPS
ROOT --> MKT
TECH --> TECH_BE
TECH --> TECH_FE
TECH --> TECH_AI
OPS --> OPS_A
MKT --> MKT_PLAN

note bottom of ROOT
组织标签层级结构
支持多级嵌套
end note

@enduml
